**Last Living Baby Wolf** | Solo Miscellaneous - Werewolf Team | Temporary & Transformation
__Basics__
The Last Living Baby Wolf can only be in the game when there is no werewolf team. 
__Details__
The Last Living Baby Wolf is a result of a player joining the last living wolf without copying it. This can be the result of the last living wolf infecting another player by having chosen infecting wolf as one of their three roles.
